skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: inspire me
des:
Get inspired with an assortment of top quotes from historical figures and business leaders. When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next quote. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
